\displaystyle\sum_k \left(\frac{1}{2}\right)^k
\left(|a^{1/k}-1|\right)^k=\left(|\exp\left(\frac 1 k\log a\right)-1|\right)^k\sim_\infty\left(\frac{|\log a|}{k}\right)^k<\left(\frac{1}{2}\right)^k\quad\text{for large $k$}
